CAUTION !!!!!!!!!!! CAUTION !!!!!!

############
No guarantee is provided if you do NOT take care while wiring the Pi with the
breadboard. Exercise due diligence before powering the pi with the circuit assembled.
############

Examples are using either one of the following sketches to construct the circuit.

gpio_bcm_board : ../model_bplus_bcm_board_sketch.png
gpio_bcm       : ../model_bplus_gpio_pinout_sketch.png

In the example, refer to the comment "gpio_bcm_board" or "gpio_bcm" and 
accordingly place the wires to connect the components on the breadboard and 
Raspberry Pi Model B+ Rev1.2

